flowchart TD
    COMMIT[Commit/Push] --> LINT{Lint<br/>zero warnings}
    LINT -->|passou| TYPE{Typecheck<br/>sem erros}
    LINT -->|falhou| FAIL1[FAIL]
    TYPE -->|passou| COV{Cobertura<br/>maior ou igual 80}
    TYPE -->|falhou| FAIL2[FAIL]
    COV -->|passou| SEC{Seguranca<br/>sem alerts}
    COV -->|falhou| FAIL3[FAIL]
    SEC -->|passou| BUILD[Build]
    SEC -->|falhou| FAIL4[FAIL]